    "Html": "How do you align column data in WPF DataGrid?  I have the following code below and seems to work for Right alignment, but Center will not work.  Any solutions?<br>\r\n<span style=\"color:#40c4ff\">\r\n<p>&lt;wpftk:DataGridTextColumn Header=&quot;Cost ( $ )&quot;<br>\r\n                                                Width=&quot;70&quot; <br>\r\n                                                Binding=&quot;{Binding Cost, StringFormat=\\{0:0.00\\}}&quot;&gt;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\">&lt;wpftk:DataGridTextColumn.CellStyle&gt;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt 0.5in\">&lt;Style TargetType=&quot;{x:Type wpftk:DataGridCell}&quot;&gt;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt 1in\">&lt;Setter Property=&quot;HorizontalAlignment&quot; Value=&quot;<b><span style=\"font-size:14pt\">Center</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt 0.5in\">&lt;/Style&gt;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\">&lt;/wpftk:DataGridTextColumn.CellStyle&gt;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0pt\">&lt;/wpftk:DataGridTextColumn&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#40c4ff\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n",
    "PostedDate": "2009-02-12T07:40:36.97-08:00",
    "UserRole": null,
    "MarkedAsAnswerDate": null
  },
