    "Html": "Shaggygi<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTry this it seems to work for me<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&lt;wpftk:DataGridTextColumn.CellStyle&gt;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;Style TargetType=&quot;{x:Type wpftk:DataGridCell}&quot; &gt;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>&lt;Setter Property=&quot;TextBlock.TextAlignment&quot; Value=&quot;Center&quot; /&gt;</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;Setter Property=&quot;TextBlock.VerticalAlignment&quot; Value=&quot;Center&quot;/&gt;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;/Style&gt;<br>\r\n&lt;/wpftk:DataGridTextColumn.CellStyle&gt;\r\n",
    "PostedDate": "2009-02-12T15:27:39.627-08:00",
